## Authentication

Firebase Authentication via `react-firebase-hooks`. Auth state managed via Redux `authSlice` + `react-firebase-hooks`.

```typescript
// Auth context usage
const { user, loading } = useAuth();

// Firebase hooks
const [signIn, user, loading, error] = useSignInWithEmailAndPassword(auth);
const [createUser] = useCreateUserWithEmailAndPassword(auth);
```

