## Date Utilities

All date formatting goes through `web/src/utils/dateUtils.ts`. Never format dates inline.

```typescript
import { formatDate, formatDateWithOptions } from '../utils/dateUtils';

formatDate(firebaseTimestamp);                          // "12/15/2023"
formatDateWithOptions(firebaseTimestamp, 'MMM d, yyyy'); // "Dec 15, 2023"
```

Handles Firebase `Timestamp` objects (with `toDate()`), raw `{ _seconds, _nanoseconds }` objects, `Date` objects, ISO strings, and `null`/`undefined`.

